---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<BaseLayout title="About — Jaison" description="About me and what I do">
  <div class="about prose">
    <section>
      <h1>About</h1>

      <p>
        I'm Jaison. I build things with code and write about it here.
      </p>

      <p>
        Right now I'm spending most of my time on AI — specifically how to use it
        as a real tool, not just a novelty. I built a personal AI assistant that
        runs 24/7, handles scheduling, monitors news, and keeps me organized.
        It's one of those projects that started as "let me try this" and turned
        into something I actually rely on every day.
      </p>

      <p>
        I also follow crypto pretty closely. Not the speculation side so much as
        the infrastructure — what's actually being built, what problems DeFi and
        Web3 are solving that couldn't be solved before.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>This site</h2>

      <p>
        Built with <a href="https://astro.build">Astro</a> and
        <a href="https://tailwindcss.com">Tailwind</a>, hosted on Cloudflare Pages.
        The design is inspired by
        <a href="https://www.benkuhn.net">Ben Kuhn</a>,
        <a href="https://www.natebjones.com">Nate B Jones</a>, and
        <a href="https://paulstamatiou.com">Paul Stamatiou</a>.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="links-section">
      <h2>Elsewhere</h2>

      <div class="link-list">
        <a href="https://twitter.com/binnsjaison">Twitter</a>
        <a href="https://github.com/JaisonBinns">GitHub</a>
        <a href="https://tiktok.com/@heyjaison">TikTok</a>
        <a href="https://instagram.com/heyjaison">Instagram</a>
        <a href="https://jaisonbinns.substack.com">Substack</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about {
    max-width: none;
  }

  .about section {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .about section:first-child {
    padding-top: 1rem;
  }

  .about h1 {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .about h2 {
    margin-top: 0;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .link-list {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .link-list a {
    color: var(--accent);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    transition: color 0.3s;
  }

  .link-list a:hover {
    color: var(--accent-hover);
  }
</style>
